<BLOCKQUOTE><P>Welcome to Central Vermont Public Service Corp., an
independent, investor-owned company providing energy and energy-related services
to customers in nearly three-quarters of the towns, villages and cities of
Vermont. About half of the state's 567,000 residents receive service from CV,
the largest of the state's 22 utilities. Through a subsidiary, Connecticut
Valley Electric Company, Inc., 10,000 customers are served in 13 towns in New
Hampshire.
</P></BLOCKQUOTE>  
