VALIGN="MIDDLE" ALIGN="LEFT" COLSTART="2"><UL><h3><LI>Be careful in using humidifiers. Excessive humidity causes excessive
condensation on windows, in wall cavities, and in attics (where you may see
frost on nails). Mold and mildew may start to grow if humidity is too high.
These effects are detrimental to the building structure and possibly to your
health.<BR><BR></LI>
